summary:
Currently, I work for Booking.com. I am responsible for the infrastructure of our SAP systems.

Before I worked for Sabris as a basis consultant, I was responsible for installing, configuring, and maintaining both operating systems and SAP systems. Apart from that, I cooperated on the development of our internal information system where I gained experience with development in SAP systems.
